- Should you wish to designate a child/children as your Primary or Contingent Beneficiary, we recommend that you also name a Trustee (see definition below). Should you choose to designate a trustee for minor children refer to page 2 of the form and indicate the First, Middle and Last Name, Date of Birth or Age, Percent of Benefit to be paid in the event of your passing, and if the proceeds will be Revocable or Irrevocable for each individual(s) that you wish to name as beneficiary(ies) ;

